---
import { Phone, Github, Coffee } from 'lucide-astro';
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="w-full bg-[#f2efe4] border-t-2 border-[#0f1f19] mt-auto py-12 text-brand-body">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 64 64"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <rect x="10" y="10" width="52" height="52" rx="12" fill="#0f1f19" />
            <rect x="6" y="6" width="52" height="52" rx="12" fill="#065f46" stroke="#0f1f19" stroke-width="3.5" />
            <rect x="24" y="15" width="16" height="4" rx="1.5" fill="#faf9f4" stroke="#0f1f19" stroke-width="2.5" />
            <rect x="27" y="19" width="10" height="4" fill="#faf9f4" stroke="#0f1f19" stroke-width="2.5" />
            <rect x="18" y="23" width="28" height="26" rx="6" fill="#faf9f4" stroke="#0f1f19" stroke-width="3" />
            <path d="M26 36H38M32 30V42" stroke="#e8632c" stroke-width="4.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
          </svg>
          <span class="font-bold text-[#0f1f19] font-heading">FarmaTurno Chile</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Buscador de farmacias de turno nacionales y gestor personal de medicamentos. Desarrollado
          como evidencia evaluativa para la Unidad 3 de INACAP (SPA con React + Islas de Astro).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-[#0f1f19] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
          Teléfonos de Emergencia
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs font-mono">
          <li>
            <a
              href="tel:131"
              class="hover:text-[#065f46] transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium"
            >
              <Phone class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> SAMU (Ambulancia): <strong>131</strong>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="tel:133"
              class="hover:text-[#065f46] transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium"
            >
              <Phone class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Carabineros de Chile: <strong>133</strong>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="tel:6003607777"
              class="hover:text-[#065f46] transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium"
            >
              <Phone class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Salud Responde (MINSAL): <strong>600 360 7777</strong>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold font-mono text-[#0f1f19] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
          Fuentes & Tecnología
        </h4>
        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed">
          Los datos de farmacias de turno son obtenidos en tiempo real del endpoint público oficial
          de la Subsecretaría de Redes Asistenciales, Ministerio de Salud de Chile (MINSAL). El
          catálogo de medicamentos proviene del Instituto de Salud Pública (ISP) y CENABAST.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="border-t-2 border-[#0f1f19] pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between text-[11px] gap-4"
    >
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} FarmaTurno Chile. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/politica-de-privacidad"
          class="font-mono uppercase tracking-wide hover:text-[#065f46] transition-colors"
        >
          Política de Privacidad
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/vngerus"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono uppercase tracking-wide hover:text-[#065f46] transition-colors"
          title="GitHub Sponsors"
        >
          <Github class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Sponsor
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://ko-fi.com/vngerus"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono uppercase tracking-wide hover:text-[#065f46] transition-colors"
          title="Ko-fi"
        >
          <Coffee class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Ko-fi
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
